# Quorum Databases
Host db-quorum-dev
    LocalForward 5433 quorum-production-updating.ck4wgl7u5wcg.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com:5432

Host db-quorum-prod
    LocalForward 5434 quorum-production.ck4wgl7u5wcg.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com:5432

